ciscoCableL2vpnMIB.name: ciscoCableL2vpnMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoCableL2vpnMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-ubr@cisco.com
ciscoCableL2vpnMIB.description: This MIB module defines managed objects that facilitate the management of Cisco devices complying to the DOCSIS L2VPN Feature for IP/MPLS pseudo-wire. The Cisco CMTS implementation of IP/MPLS pseudo-wire is based on DOCSIS BSOD L2VPN specification. The information available through this MIB includes: Mapping information between various configuration of the pseudo-wire pertaining to DOCSIS BSOD L2VPN. The MIB tables implemented give quick access to information using either Cable Modem MAC address/VPN, peer IP address/VCID or L2vpnIndex as index in tables. Glossary: CMTS - Cable Modem Termination System VCID - Virtual Circuit Identifier MPLS - Multi-Protocol Label Switching AToM - Any Transport Over MPLS DOCSIS - Data over Cable Service Interface Specification BSOD - Business Services over DOCSIS L2VPN - Layer 2 Virtual Private Network pseudo-wire - Layer 2 connection over IP/MPLS backbone

CiscoCableL2vpnIndex.name: CiscoCableL2vpnIndex
CiscoCableL2vpnIndex.description: An integer value locally generated by the CMTS for each known pseudo-wire. It is intended to be used as a short index for tables in this MIB module. This index is allocated at runtime from a pool of indices for each pseudo-wire and is unique to that pseudo-wire only between every creation and deletion of that pseudo-wire.

ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexTable.name: ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexTable
ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexTable.description: Every L2VPN provisioned Cable Modem can be a part of multiple VPNs and the CMTS assigns a L2vpnIndex for each {Cable Modem MAC address, VPN-id} pair. This table maps {Cable Modem MAC address, VPN-id} to the L2vpnIndex.

ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexEntry.name: ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexEntry
ccl2vpnMacVpnIdL2vpnIndexEntry.description: Each row contains the Cable Modem MAC address and VPN identifier and the corresponding L2vpnIndex. Entry in this table is populated for each one of the pseudo-wire provisioned on the CMTS.

ccl2vpnMac.name: ccl2vpnMac
ccl2vpnMac.description: This object identifies the Cable Modem MAC address.

ccl2vpnVpnId.name: ccl2vpnVpnId
ccl2vpnVpnId.description: This object identifies the VPN provisioned for L2VPN Cable Modem.

ccl2vpnMacVpnIdToL2vpnIndex.name: ccl2vpnMacVpnIdToL2vpnIndex
ccl2vpnMacVpnIdToL2vpnIndex.description: This object identifies the L2vpnIndex assigned for this Cable Modem MAC Address/VPN pair by the CMTS.

ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexTable.name: ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexTable
ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexTable.description: Every L2VPN Cable Modem can be provisioned with multiple VPNs and for each {Cable Modem MAC address, VPN-id} pair, there is a IP/MPLS pseudo-wire established. The pseudo-wire is specified by {peer IP address, VCID}. This table maps {peer IP address, VCID} to the L2vpnIndex.

ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexEntry.name: ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexEntry
ccl2vpnPWL2vpnIndexEntry.description: Each row contains the pseudo-wire peer IP address and Virtual Circuit Identifier (VCID) and the corresponding L2vpnIndex. Entry in this table is populated for each one of the pseudo-wire provisioned on the CMTS.

ccl2vpnPseudoWireType.name: ccl2vpnPseudoWireType
ccl2vpnPseudoWireType.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire type.

ccl2vpnPeerIPAddressType.name: ccl2vpnPeerIPAddressType
ccl2vpnPeerIPAddressType.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire peer IP address type provisioned for L2VPN.

ccl2vpnPeerIPAddress.name: ccl2vpnPeerIPAddress
ccl2vpnPeerIPAddress.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire peer IP address provisioned for L2VPN. The type of this address is determined by the value of ccl2vpnPeerIPAddressType object.

ccl2vpnVCID.name: ccl2vpnVCID
ccl2vpnVCID.description: This object identifies the Virtual Circuit Identifier (VCID) of the pseudo-wire.

ccl2vpnPWToL2vpnIndex.name: ccl2vpnPWToL2vpnIndex
ccl2vpnPWToL2vpnIndex.description: This object identifies the L2vpnIndex assigned by CMTS for this pseudo-wire peer IP address/VCID pair and for this Cable Modem MAC Address/VPN.

ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWTable.name: ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWTable
ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWTable.description: For every VPN provisioned for the L2VPN Cable Modem, the CMTS establishes pseudo-wire. This table maps L2vpnIndex to pseudo-wire configuration parameters.

ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWEntry.name: ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWEntry
ccl2vpnL2vpnIndexPWEntry.description: Each row contains the L2vpnIndex for the pseudo-wire and the corresponding configuration paramters including the Cable Modem MAC address, VPN identifier, peer IP address, Virtual Circuit Identifier (VCID) and pseudo-wire type. Entry in this table is populated for each one of the pseudo-wire provisioned on the CMTS.

ccl2vpnL2vpnIndex.name: ccl2vpnL2vpnIndex
ccl2vpnL2vpnIndex.description: This object identifies the L2vpnIndex assigned for this Cable Modem MAC Address/VPN pair by the CMTS.

ccl2vpnPWMAC.name: ccl2vpnPWMAC
ccl2vpnPWMAC.description: This object identifies the Cable Modem MAC address.

ccl2vpnPWVpnId.name: ccl2vpnPWVpnId
ccl2vpnPWVpnId.description: This object identifies the VPN Identifier provisioned for L2VPN Cable Modem.

ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddressType.name: ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddressType
ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddressType.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire peer IP address type.

ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddress.name: ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddress
ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddress.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire peer IP address. The type of this address is determined by the value of ccl2vpnPWPeerIPAddressType object.

ccl2vpnPWType.name: ccl2vpnPWType
ccl2vpnPWType.description: This object identifies the pseudo-wire type.

ccl2vpnPWVCID.name: ccl2vpnPWVCID
ccl2vpnPWVCID.description: This object identifies the Virtual Circuit Identifier (VCID) for pseudo-wire.

ccl2vpnMIBCompliance.name: ccl2vpnMIBCompliance
ccl2vpnMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for the CISCO-CABLE-L2VPN-MIB.

ccl2vpnPWMappingGroup.name: ccl2vpnPWMappingGroup
ccl2vpnPWMappingGroup.description: A collection of objects providing Cable L2VPN pseudo-wire configuration.
